Dubov Ilya Roydovich EXPERIENCE OF FREEFEM++ AND NETGEN USAGE IN THE SIMULATION PROGRAM FOR AERODYNAMIC PROCESSES <p>The article describes the experience of using of the open source libraries such as Freefem++ and NetGen to develop a simulation program for aerodynamic processes. Using of these libraries can reduce development time, but it is necessary to solve some technical problems that are described in the article.</p> Simulation, software, aerodynamics, cleanroom; 2014-05-01
